snippet.title: Evercade Interplay 'Collection 1' Cartridge Trailer
snippet.description:
Visit: http://evercade.co.uk/interplay-collection-1-cartridge/

The Interplay Collection 1 cartridge brings 6 classic Interplay games to the Evercade, including: Earthworm Jim, Clayfighter, Boogerman, Battle Chess and more! The cartridge will be supplied in a stunning collectable retro style physical case.

Full games list:
1. Earthworm Jim
2. Clayfighter
3. Boogerman
4. BattleChess
5. Incantation
6. Titan
